videos.headline: Lamar Jordan scores third TD of first quarter
videos.description: New Mexico QB Lamar Jordan breaks free for a 52-yard touchdown run, his third touchdown of the first quarter for the Lobos.

videos.headline: Rutgers responds with 75-yard TD pass
videos.description: After falling behind 21-0, Rutgers QB Chris Laviano hits Jawuan Harris for a 75-yard touchdown to put the Scarlet Knights on the board.

videos.headline: Offensive trickery pays off for Rutgers
videos.description: Rutgers gets within one score of New Mexico thanks to Rutgers WR Janarion Grant taking the pitch and connecting with Andre Patton for the 21-yard score.

videos.headline: Rutgers RB breaks free for 80-yard TD run
videos.description: Rutgers RB Robert Martin bursts through the middle for an 80-yard touchdown run.
